	tion: Mercer Island Community Center 8236 SE 24th Street\, Mercer Island\,
	 WA 98040 Parking: Free When: Tuesday\, March 31st\, 2026﻿ ﻿Time: 11am to 
	1pm Matchmaking Your Business is a structured\, high-energy networking eve
	nt designed to connect Realtors with trusted industry vendors. The goal is
	 simple: Help Realtors build reliable vendor partnerships that elevate the
	 client experience\, streamline transactions\, and support long-term busin
	ess growth. Tired of calling vendor after vendor trying to find someone re
	liable for your clients? Come meet them in one place. Our WCR Seattle Metr
	o Vendor Speed Networking Event gives you the chance to connect one-on-one
	 with trusted industry professionals who can help support your business an
	d your clients. Build your network. Save time. Strengthen your resources. 
	Just real connections that build your book of business. Come ready to conn
	ect\, collaborate\, and fine the right matches for your business.\n\nhttps
